wiki.summary: Written & recorded in Finland during the bitter winter of 2009. This is a special Finland-mini album differing from the other DTL releases as it was composed and recorded by the Finnish line-up that played on the minitour back in 2009. Line-up: Azgorh - Vocals Stormheit - Drums Molestor Kadotus - Bass Shatraug - Guitars Read more on Last.fm.
